title: 1v5 Penta Kill Evelynn | Rank 26 Evelynn One Trick

embed.description: Hiya :) Getting a Penta on a champion you love feels sooo good, especially a 1v5 five... even if it is a unofficial one T_T Stream: https://mixer.com/CynderIsAwkward Music: Before My Body is Dry - BakaRadio || Styx Helix - JPN NIGHTCORE

body:
Hiya :)

So based on everyone's feedback from the last video, I have made the music much quieter and less bangy (if you get what I mean?).

If you have any tips or advice, I would love to hear :D

replies.body:
Doesn't mean I can't make videos to entertain people.

But trust me, I'm trying my best to improve. At least making videos means I watch replays.
Of course you can but where does the "rank 26" come from :') It is a good video
It came from the fact that I was ranked 26th in terms of Mastery Points on Evelynn. Now I'm #24
